Richard H. Lenny Joins FFL
May 18, 2011



Share:




 



Richard H. Lenny has joined Friedman Fleischer & Lowe as an operating partner. Mr. Lenny will provide management and operating expertise to the firm's portfolio companies, as well as help identify and evaluate new investment opportunities in the consumer products sector. He has previously served as chairman and CEO of The Hershey Company.













